data.description: This home has a ZERO-DOWN-PAYMENT 100% financing option through United Community Bank Mortgage Services. Take a look at this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home in the friendly subdivision of Twin Oaks. Centered in a great location within Calhoun, you will have easy access to I-75 while shopping and dining are also close by. This home boasts high ceilings and an inviting living room area that includes a gas log fireplace. The spacious kitchen offers plenty of counter space and features stainless steel appliances. All appliances, including the Samsung Smart refrigerator, stay with the home. The master bedroom features a large bay window which offers a great view of the neighborhood. The large master bathroom has a jetted soaking tub, separate shower, and walk-in closet. Two other  bedrooms are located on the opposite side of the home along with the second bathroom. There is also a partially finished basement that offers a laundry room (washer and dryer stay with the home) and another separate room that can be used as a gym, office, playroom, or den area. The 2 car garage enters into the basement area. This home has a new electric water heater and there is NO HOA! Schedule your tour today! Home is occupied, please do not disturb occupants!
